text: Skellington may refer to: * Skellington Productions, a film production company * Jack Skellington, a character from the 1993 film The Nightmare Before Christmas * Skellington (band) * Skellington (album), a 1989 album by Julian Cope * Skellington 3, a 2018 album by Julian Cope ==See also== * "Skelington", a song by British Jazz Rock band Colosseum, originally from their 1971 album Colosseum Live * Skillington, a village and civil parish in Lincolnshire, England
